race.comment: ARCTIC CROP (8) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in second (17.66) behind Forever Seven at Northam. Can measure up this time. SILLY OLD BEAR (2) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at this track over 300m behind Aeroplane Penny (18.03) in a Grade 5/6. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. One of the better hopes. MUM'S A HOOT (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (16.86) last time in a Grade 6 at Cannington. Has ability and can measure up. BUDDY'S MATE (4) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
